procstep.procdesc: The tax parcel polygons are constructed from mapped parcel boundary lines. The boundary lines are mapped based on a variety of source maps including certified surveys, subdivision plats, legal descriptions, and historic tax maps. The source material dates range from the early 1900's to the present.
